      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=cz6h4y1zty]{color:#4269b8} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=cz6h4y1zty]{color:#476ebd}[data-colorid=g6w7jh3ve2]{color:#4269b8} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=g6w7jh3ve2]{color:#476ebd}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p local-id=\"854c535309bc\"><br /></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642517/RenderManStudio_Header_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433103668&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=486\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642517/RenderManStudio_Header_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433103668&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"692\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544642567\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManStudio_Header_1.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544642517\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"b0fc5af7-40aa-4fd0-9a0b-ecacc3e97742\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642517/RenderManStudio_Header_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433103668&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1800&amp;height=972 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642517/RenderManStudio_Header_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433103668&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=486 1x\" /></span><p local-id=\"22d2209b8252\">Welcome to the new and exciting Solaris / USD example scene - The RenderMan Digital Studio</p><p local-id=\"711d8c26929b\"><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://downloads.renderman.pixar.com/renderman-examples/R27/RfS/SolarisDemoScene.zip\" rel=\"nofollow\">Download</a><br /><br />The scene is fully stocked with all sorts of studio-inspired assets and kits, kindly supplied to us by RenderMan's in-house rental company, <br />Point Reyes Electric, is ready for you to create your studio environments and works in both RIS and XPU, and denoise ready!<br /><br />Most of the assets in the studio have a variety of model and shading variants.<br /><br /></p><p local-id=\"01017525d6a1\">The scene comes in two flavors.&nbsp;<br /><br /></p><hr local-id=\"cced84f6233f\" /><p local-id=\"c1bac8370437\"><br /><strong><span data-colorid=\"cz6h4y1zty\">RenderMan Studio / Asset Assembly</span></strong><br />The first setup is the base assembly where all the assets are in their default positions, ready for you to arrange into your bespoke own studio setup.</p><p local-id=\"f2d186970c15\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642517/RenderMan_Solaris_RenderManStudio_BaseScene.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433103342&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642517/RenderMan_Solaris_RenderManStudio_BaseScene.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433103342&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544642555\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_RenderManStudio_BaseScene.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544642517\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"13706162-a55d-443f-8aa5-c2f792c19356\" data-media-type=\"file\" /></span><br /><br />The files for this setup are :<br /><br /><strong>Solaris / Houdini File :</strong><br />RenderManStudio_Assembly_v01.hip<br /><br /><strong>USD Layer :</strong><br />/usd/Assembly/RenderManStudio_Assembly_v01.usda<br /><br /></p><hr local-id=\"8118bd9848b7\" /><p local-id=\"51b49cc65227\"><br /><strong><span data-colorid=\"g6w7jh3ve2\">RenderMan Studio / Layout &amp; Lighting</span></strong><br />The second setup is a layout we have created for you to quickly begin having fun with and inserting your own props.<br /><br /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642517/RenderManStudio_Lighting.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433103497&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642517/RenderManStudio_Lighting.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433103497&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544642558\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManStudio_Lighting.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544642517\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"a8ef5109-ec11-42cb-a5bf-b6b12873e0d6\" data-media-type=\"file\" /></span><br /><br />The files for this setup are :</p><p local-id=\"9d4d58c0e40f\"><strong>Layout</strong><br /><strong>Solaris / Houdini File :</strong><br />RenderManStudio_Layout_v01.hip<br /><br /><strong>USD Layer :</strong><br />/usd/layout/RenderManStudio_Layout_v01.usda<br /><br /><strong>Lighting &amp; Rendering</strong><br /><strong>Solaris / Houdini File :</strong><br />RenderManStudio_Lighting_v01.hip<br /><br /><strong>USD Layer :</strong><br />/usd/layout/RenderManStudio_Lighting_v01.usda<br /><br /></p><hr local-id=\"9c6a41833de5\" /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"632\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642517/RenderManStudio_Close_Lighting.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433103497&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=632&amp;height=355\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642517/RenderManStudio_Close_Lighting.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433103497&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"720\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544642561\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManStudio_Close_Lighting.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544642517\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"40ff0af1-e6db-4c20-a6bb-874279ca2972\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642517/RenderManStudio_Close_Lighting.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433103497&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1264&amp;height=710 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642517/RenderManStudio_Close_Lighting.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433103497&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=632&amp;height=355 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-right-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-right\" width=\"632\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642517/RenderManStudio_Wide_Lighting.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433103497&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=632&amp;height=355\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642517/RenderManStudio_Wide_Lighting.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433103497&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"720\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544642564\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManStudio_Wide_Lighting.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544642517\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"a1e2ab4e-8ac1-4433-93df-a689cc8552bd\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642517/RenderManStudio_Wide_Lighting.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433103497&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1264&amp;height=710 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642517/RenderManStudio_Wide_Lighting.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433103497&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=632&amp;height=355 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"680\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642517/RenderMan_FlightCase_LookDev2.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433103177&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=680&amp;height=382\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642517/RenderMan_FlightCase_LookDev2.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433103177&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"450\" data-width=\"800\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544642546\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_FlightCase_LookDev2.gif\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/gif\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544642517\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"ba21b7d8-4afe-4787-9fae-f4df6844f7c8\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642517/RenderMan_FlightCase_LookDev2.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433103177&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=800&amp;height=450 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642517/RenderMan_FlightCase_LookDev2.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433103177&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=680&amp;height=382 1x\" /></span><hr local-id=\"7a4919b63492\" /><p local-id=\"c7bfd719dca6\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />Version 1.0 of the RenderMan Studio in the Houdini / USD format can be downloaded here: <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://downloads.renderman.pixar.com/renderman-examples/R25/Solaris/Studio-Solaris.zip\" rel=\"nofollow\">Studio-Solaris.zip</a><br /><br /></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Logo.jpg\" width=\"250\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642517/Logo.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433102924&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=250&amp;height=250\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642517/Logo.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433102924&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"500\" data-width=\"500\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544642531\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Logo.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544642517\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"5ac36829-efad-46b9-9db8-b32599878dbf\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642517/Logo.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433102924&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=500&amp;height=500 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642517/Logo.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433102924&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=250&amp;height=250 1x\" /></span><p local-id=\"22c992aa968d\"><br /></p><p local-id=\"0d966d50e626\"><br /></p><p local-id=\"0bf108b95796\"><br /></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
